          "title": "Zanzibar — Beach (Kiwengwa)",
          "body": "Stay: Ayla Beach House, Kiwengwa, 4 nights. North coast (Nungwi area) offers more consistent swimming conditions vs. east/south where low tide limits access. Zanzibar local driving permit required (~$15, valid up to 3 months). Vasilis holds an IDP — most rental companies arrange the local permit with license photo 24+ hours before. Police checkpoints are frequent; carry both IDP and local permit (screenshot acceptable).",
