          "body": "EgyptAir DAR→CAI, 05:20–11:05. Stay: Ramses Hilton, 1 night. Sightseeing: Islamic Cairo, the Citadel, Khan el-Khalili bazaar, Coptic Cairo. Taxi needed between Citadel and Coptic Cairo. Fly home Aug 20: Aegean A3935 CAI→ATH, 19:55–22:00, ref ZZL22S.",
