        {
          "id": "1b9c173f-5cc3-4348-8668-489496c6a2cf",
          "date": "Aug 3-20",
          "title": "Trip Summary & Key Learnings",
          "body": "Full trip: Aug 3-20, 2026. Vasileios Kefallinos + Athina Mari. Cairo → Arusha → Tanzania safari circuit → Zanzibar → Dar es Salaam. Total flights: ~€2,707 (6 legs). Total lodging (excl. safari): ~$951. Safari: $1,200. Key tips: EgyptAir operates Cairo↔Dar — confirmed. Tanzania e-visa mandatory online ($50/person). Egypt e-visa multiple-entry ($65), printed copy mandatory. Ngorongoro nights are cold. Zanzibar: north coast best for swimming. Precision Air: soft bags preferred. August is peak safari season — ideal for Great Wildebeest Migration. Vasilis prefers simple, concise output (bullet lists over tables).",
          "category": "note",
          "location": "Multi-city",
          "contacts": "",
          "origin": "tanzaniamemories.md"
        }
